high_descs: Move to the arm chair to the left of the piano
Pick up the pillow from the arm chair.
Move to the ottoman in front of the same arm chair
Place the pillow on the ottoman in front of the same arm chair.
Move to the couch behind you
Pick up the pillow off the couch
Move to the ottoman in front of the arm chair
Place the pillow on the ottoman next to the other one
anns.task_desc: Place two different pillows from the room onto the ottoman in front of the arm chair.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the tv then turn right and walk to the wall then turn right to face the black chair.
Pick up the plaid pillow off of the black chair.
Turn right and walk past the ottoman and then turn left and take a step then turn left to face the ottoman so you are facing the chair and the wall behind it.
Put the pillow on the ottoman.
Turn around and walk a step then turn left so you are facing a black couch with a plaid pillow on it.
Pick up the plaid pillow.
Walk back to where you put the first plaid pillow.
Set this pillow to the left of the other pillow.
anns.task_desc: Put two plaid pillows on the ottoman.

high_descs: Take a few steps to the left and face the chair.
Pick the plaid pillow up from the chair.
Turn towards the ottoman.
Put the plaid pillow on the ottoman perpendicular to the chair on top of the gray rectangular.
Turn around and head to the left side of the couch.
Pick the plaid pillow up from the couch.
Turn back around to the ottoman.
Set the pillow down on the ottoman to the left of the first pillow and perpendicular to the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put two plaid pillows on the ottoman at a perpendicular angle to the chair.
